name: Kooky Cooking Simulator
description:
You are WheelFrog.

You are helping a new advanced AI known as A-Eye to cook, but A-Eye seems to have lost his ingredients in the warehouse.

Navigate the maze to help A-Eye find his ingredients to make the best delicacy ever.

Instructions:

ARROW KEYS - MOVE

Z - INTERACT

SEARCH THE MAZE TO FIND THE INGREDIENT INSTRUCTED BY A-EYE AND RETURN IT TO HIS COOKING POT.

SUBMISSION FOR WOWIE JAM 4.0 WITH THE THEME "COLLABORATE WITH AI"!
